{"tid":1840121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你仲記唔記得四年前嘅年初一？今年年初一你會做啲咩？","createTime":"2020-01-24T17:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T17:53:36.000Z","uid":240531,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db058d90e761df571f73e388e4ccd409b3e91032","tid":1840121,"uid":240531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"四年前嘅魚蛋革命，你仲記唔記得？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYAQkSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYAQkSF.jpg&h=b4c19396&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvgLUcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvgLUcG.jpg&h=0f8a8fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9foRPL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9foRPL1.jpg&h=4ce9b88b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/As73FSH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAs73FSH.jpg&h=7d0c938f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四年後，我哋經歷咗場反送中運動<br />\n五大訴求仲未爭取到<br />\n但好多手足都被拉、被打、被自殺<br />\n有人話場運動降咗溫，甚至完咗<br />\n但我好希望你諗返起四年前嘅手足<br />\n諗返起呢七個月犧牲咗嘅手足<br />\n年初一去旺角 食返串魚蛋<br />\n話俾大家聽我哋冇忘記到<br />\n場運動仲未完㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtON7xH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtON7xH.jpg&h=58343b07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ntyiEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ntyiEo.jpg&h=18622b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，保護自己同其他人 記住帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097fd20a646130105fd2a78bffc00a75a868d8cf","tid":1840121,"uid":258133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7114fb94252117f2e92c8a6e84e7cda46a850105","tid":1840121,"uid":258133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68250184bf1f5132ebe4